<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTA66">
<l>cūṭṭāya nēmiyāṉ ṟollarakka ṉiṉṉuyirai</l>
<l>māṭṭē tuyariḻaitta māyavaṉai yīṭṭa</l>
<l>veṟikoṇṭa taṇṭuḻāy vētiyaṉai neñcē</l>
<l>yaṟikaṇṭāy coṉṉē ṉatu.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The Dark one who by his discus that was hot, made the life</l>
<l>of the old Rakṣasa a misery in that place, the Veda [expert]</l>
<l>with cool Tulsi that has taken a vigorous scent, o heart,</l>
<l>know [him], see. I have said that.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
